{"key":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01|Eph|3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","chapter":3,"textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024","parserRevision":"v11","verses":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:1","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":3,"verse":1,"text":"For this reason, I, Paul, the prisoner of Christ Jesus on behalf of you Gentiles —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:2","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":3,"verse":2,"text":"assuming you have heard about the administration of God’s grace that he gave me for you.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:3","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":3,"verse":3,"text":"The mystery was made known to me by revelation, as I have briefly written above.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:4","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":3,"verse":4,"text":"By reading this you are able to understand my insight into the mystery of Christ.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:5","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":3,"verse":5,"text":"This was not made known to people in other generations as it is now revealed to his holy apostles and prophets by the Spirit:","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:6","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":3,"verse":6,"text":"The Gentiles are coheirs, members of the same body, and partners in the promise in Christ Jesus through the gospel.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:7","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":3,"verse":7,"text":"I was made a servant of this gospel by the gift of God’s grace that was given to me by the working of his power.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:8","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":3,"verse":8,"text":"This grace was given to me —the least of all the saints —to proclaim to the Gentiles the incalculable riches of Christ,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:9","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":3,"verse":9,"text":"and to shed light for all about the administration of the mystery hidden for ages in God who created all things.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:10","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":3,"verse":10,"text":"This is so that God’s multi-faceted wisdom may now be made known through the church to the rulers and authorities in the heavens.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:11","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":3,"verse":11,"text":"This is according to his eternal purpose accomplished in Christ Jesus our Lord.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:12","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":3,"verse":12,"text":"In him we have boldness and confident access through faith in him.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:13","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":3,"verse":13,"text":"So, then, I ask you not to be discouraged over my afflictions on your behalf, for they are your glory.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:14","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":3,"verse":14,"text":"For this reason I kneel before the Father","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:15","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":3,"verse":15,"text":"from whom every family in heaven and on earth is named.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:16","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":3,"verse":16,"text":"I pray that he may grant you, according to the riches of his glory, to be strengthened with power in your inner being through his Spirit,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:17","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":3,"verse":17,"text":"and that Christ may dwell in your hearts through faith. I pray that you, being rooted and firmly established in love,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:18","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":3,"verse":18,"text":"may be able to comprehend with all the saints what is the length and width, height and depth of God’s love,","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:19","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":3,"verse":19,"text":"and to know Christ’s love that surpasses knowledge, so that you may be filled with all the fullness of God.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:20","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":3,"verse":20,"text":"Now to him who is able to do above and beyond all that we ask or think according to the power that works in us —","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:21","bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","bookOrder":48,"chapter":3,"verse":21,"text":"to him be glory in the church and in Christ Jesus to all generations, forever and ever. Amen.","textRevision":"api-bible-csb-2024"}],"layout":{"bibleId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01","bookAbbr":"Eph","chapter":3,"paragraphStarts":[1,8,14,20],"headings":[{"beforeVerse":1,"text":"Paul’s Ministry to the Gentiles"},{"beforeVerse":14,"text":"Prayer for Spiritual Power"}],"poetryBlocks":[],"studyByVerse":[{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:1","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For this reason, I, Paul, the prisoner "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Tm 1:8","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":8,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" of Christ Jesus on behalf of you Gentiles — "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"2Tm 1:8","book":"2Ti","chapter":1,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:2","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"assuming you have heard about the administration of God’s grace that he gave me for you. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:3","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The mystery was made known to me by revelation, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 4:13","book":"1Pe","chapter":4,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" as I have briefly written above. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Pt 4:13","book":"1Pe","chapter":4,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:4","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"By reading this you are able to understand my insight into the mystery of Christ. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Col 4:3","book":"Col","chapter":4,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Col 4:3","book":"Col","chapter":4,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Eph:3:5","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"This was not made known to people "},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit to the sons of men"},{"kind":"text","text":" in other generations as it is now revealed to his holy apostles and prophets "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 12:28–29","book":"1Co","chapter":12,"verse":28,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Eph 2:20","book":"Eph","chapter":2,"verse":20,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" by the Spirit: "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Co 12:28–29","book":"1Co","chapter":12